04:01.694 --> 04:05.322
Yeah, I've been
working on some new stuff.

04:05.323 --> 04:06.781
And I'm reading.

04:06.782 --> 04:07.991
Playing the guitar.

04:07.992 --> 04:11.661
Just kind of catching up, you know?

04:11.662 --> 04:13.788
Wow.

04:13.789 --> 04:14.956
What?

04:14.957 --> 04:17.875
Nothin... I don't know, just...

04:17.877 --> 04:19.252
you sound good.

04:19.253 --> 04:21.422
Yeah, I think I am.

04:26.761 --> 04:28.512
How's Dad?

04:28.513 --> 04:29.971
Oh, you know,

04:29.972 --> 04:31.264
same old.

04:31.265 --> 04:33.892
- Is he haunting you yet?
- No.

04:33.893 --> 04:35.435
I'm sure they had to
bring in a bigger boat

04:35.436 --> 04:37.020
to get him across the Styx, so

04:37.021 --> 04:38.815
I doubt he's even settled in.

04:41.275 --> 04:44.194
We should think about
what to do with his ashes.

04:44.195 --> 04:46.530
I read that you can
plant them in a tree.

04:46.531 --> 04:48.865
He'd probably start some arboreal plague

04:48.866 --> 04:50.909
and turn the world
into a "Mad Max" desert.

04:50.910 --> 04:53.620
Yeah, probably.

04:53.621 --> 04:56.331
Maybe we could shoot him into space?

04:57.625 --> 04:59.835
Or... I've got it,

04:59.836 --> 05:01.086
make him into fireworks.

05:01.087 --> 05:02.462
Or a pencil set.

05:11.264 --> 05:12.514
I don't know, maybe we should just

05:12.515 --> 05:16.142
bury him in my backyard.

05:16.143 --> 05:19.063
Yeah. That's probably best.

05:29.740 --> 05:31.032
Did you valet?

05:31.033 --> 05:32.617
I'm around the corner.

05:32.618 --> 05:34.828
Oh, okay.

05:34.829 --> 05:36.997
- This was fun.
- Want to get another drink?

05:39.000 --> 05:42.085
You don't have to, I just

05:42.086 --> 05:43.336
like drinking.

05:43.337 --> 05:44.588
No, totally, um...

05:44.589 --> 05:45.714
It's just getting kind of late.

05:45.715 --> 05:47.465
I've got a long day tomorrow.

05:47.466 --> 05:49.509
Oh, yeah. Me too.

05:49.510 --> 05:52.178
You know, clients.

05:52.179 --> 05:54.639
You know.

05:54.640 --> 05:56.308
- It was good to catch up.
- Yeah.

05:56.309 --> 05:57.475
Let's do it again sometime soon.

05:57.476 --> 05:59.228
Yeah, of course.

06:07.486 --> 06:09.572
- Okay. Bye.
- Bye.

